{"tid":1578514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9.21 將何妖清連儂日變做藍絲廢老同樂日 點睇","createTime":"2019-09-18T07:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T17:15:24.000Z","uid":139619,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fde00c3932f97e06596d8eb4fd65ece6292b6c5a","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 大家屌得細力d<br />\n<br />\n9.21 何妖要清連儂，見大家都好猶豫應該點做好，不如我地搞個藍絲廢老同樂日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想唔好浪費大家本身既memo同心血，會唔會可以我地提早一日將我地本身既文宣同memo收好。<br />\n然後大大隻字貼上藍絲廢老同樂區（或者有更好既名，總之要睇得出我地一早已經準備好，唔care佢地點撕）<br />\n<br />\n收錢做野100蚊區：全部貼上「再撕文宣，逢賭必輸」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收錢做野300蚊區：全部貼上「一撕文宣，絕子絕孫」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多同類文宣暫時未諗到，我地可以整唔同既獎勵區，大量印刷撕文宣受報應等字句，平時連儂得一兩張，佢地唔留意就覺得冇乜野，但如果佢地一路撕一路都睇住比人咒，唔知個心點諗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個活動有好有壞<br />\n好：唔洗浪費本身既文宣同埋寫memo既人既心血，大家睇到比人撕都冇咁心大月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；9.21藍絲都會feel到自己比人撚狗；9.22只要貼返本身既文宣上去可以極速修復連儂，話比佢地聽你地撕完對我地黎講零影響；做左野去撚班傻仔，9.21可以避免直接去同班藍絲打，睇佢地撕我地野，我地只需係屋企un un腳笑佢地<br />\n<br />\n壞：早一日去幫手收文宣同貼文宣既巴絲宣辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要大量印刷「再撕文宣」既物資<br />\n<br />\n鳩up完，唔岩玩就由個post沉啦<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"da0997e597fbb4b2dffbdc864344500b7d5a1ee5","tid":1578514,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51625e3e9c21f8932dd3976504caca3497d62fe9","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"be678ef8cad7a5c4a6e0eb41c0939a6bb65c4b66","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"593921a3d8de2340580ab22db6ec58da6b999609","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"54d038c7ad67caaad92a889b13b5afca4cc3cd25","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"03656349c0bdf6d5a0a5ef46384537455afed262","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0f83a0f42c984c0df661586cf172b6b4498cd405","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"5d8111d49a0c0a3d81f4fe3fe39a714914a05232","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"dc36d36d9f6363dee662e05e570d5b936d076a78","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"26f72e7aded94fdb392542c245c6c22655d5d62d","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"1b6544f898afd7ce614273360fbde4a86d85e72a","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"c3bbf0119e61a076aee527c37b4ecef35345799a","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"大家討論下有冇得搞笑式咁應對班藍絲<br />\n唔想開始比人覺得我地只用力量去解決班生番"},{"pid":"4bf74ac2d862949c944b93e7c914a9ac29c724a8","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"或者有其他有趣既撚狗文宣？"},{"pid":"a4abfdf530ac06a98e78fb65ea08d306188917d5","tid":1578514,"uid":282445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"都好<br />\n好過出到黎變隻揪大會"},{"pid":"c831cf3125eb27c6efb585479ef8699f9346e850","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"同埋本身巴絲痴文宣痴得好有心機，但其實印文宣都好貴，有d長青既文宣可以一直留，就咁比廢老撕左好浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f8392dddcccc5a751f8ec3292b5aaf49550a4e","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4abfdf530ac06a98e78fb65ea08d306188917d5","tid":1578514,"uid":282445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"都好<br />\n好過出到黎變隻揪大會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"我其實都讚成大家私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過9.21對家吹大雞，我亦都唔想再見到我地既人受傷同被捕<br />\n當然如果到時見到某d地點自己友多過廢老就可以hit and run然後等下一批廢老黎同樂日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf1004bcb2c7025ce73c05496e55cd058125a85","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d627b4883dcbfcac6ddb3200ae72dae4b8600d78","tid":1578514,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"到時如果成個牆都係逢賭必輸類文宣都好壯觀架"},{"pid":"703d30baa2c8c49e5e85a324339603e2b722c8da","tid":1578514,"uid":12073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"而家賭都無得賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa